#

Lemon Herb Grilled Salmon with Asparagus and Creamy Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$25
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

FishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

DinnerGourmetHealthy

Description

A zesty and flavorful grilled salmon paired with tender asparagus and rich, creamy mashed potatoes for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 4 (6 oz each)
  • Lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • Fresh dill: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • Asparagus spears: 1 pound
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • Potatoes: 2 pounds
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
